library(wesanderson)
lipdata <-read_excel("C:/Users/jessi/Desktop/Feed trial samplings_R.xlsx") #here i am assigning a name to my dataset
lipdata$sampling <-factor(lipdata$sampling)
lipdata$diet<-factor(lipdata$diet)
lipdata$tank<-factor(lipdata$tank)

arcsine_transform <- function(x) {
  asin(sqrt(x / 100))}  # Transform percentage to proportion and apply arcsine

lipdata_transformed <- lipdata %>%
  mutate(across(c(26, 28, 30, 32, 36, 37, 41), ~ arcsine_transform(.)))

s0<-lipdata %>% 
  filter(sampling=="0") #filtering data for basal sampling (sampling 0)

s1<-lipdata %>% 
  filter(sampling=="1") #filtering data for sampling 1

s2<-lipdata %>% 
  filter(sampling=="2") #filtering data for sampling 2

s0_transformed<-lipdata_transformed %>% 
  filter(sampling=="0") #filtering data for basal sampling (sampling 0)

s1_transformed<-lipdata_transformed %>% 
  filter(sampling=="1") #filtering data for sampling 1

s2_transformed<-lipdata_transformed %>% 
  filter(sampling=="2") #filtering data for sampling 2
lipwfmod <-lm(lipdata_transformed$dblipwf~lipdata_transformed$sampling,data = lipdata_transformed) # to see if lipid changes over sampling points
